	 <_manual>
This game is a simplified version of the original mastermind game.
Click on the items until you find what you think is the correct answer.
Then, click on the OK button in the control bar.
Tux gives you an indication if you got a good position by marking the item with a black box.
You can use the right mouse button to flip the colors in the oposite order.
